    <item>
      <title>苹果期待已久的 iPhone SE 大改版即将发布</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/apple-s-long-awaited-overhaul-of-budget-iphone-nears-release</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司计划在未来几天推出期待已久的 iPhone SE 改版，此举将使其低成本机型更加现代化，以刺激增长并吸引消费者从其他品牌转向iPhone SE。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/apple-s-long-awaited-overhaul-of-budget-iphone-nears-release</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 23:16:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>扎克伯格访问白宫讨论美国科技领导力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/zuckerberg-visits-white-house-to-discuss-us-tech-leadership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 首席执行官马克·扎克伯格周四访问了白宫，讨论公司如何支持特朗普政府加强美国科技领导地位的努力，公司发言人安迪·斯通 (Andy Stone) 在 X 上的一篇帖子中表示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/zuckerberg-visits-white-house-to-discuss-us-tech-leadership</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 22:52:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊的业绩是“沙袋特惠”：韦德布什的艾夫斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-06/amazon-results-are-a-sandbag-special-wedbush-s-ives-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Wedbush Securities 董事总经理兼全球科技研究主管 Dan Ives 对亚马逊第一季度的预测做出了回应。他在“Bloomberg The Close”节目中发表了讲话。亚马逊预计本季度的营业收入为 140 亿美元至 180 亿美元，低于分析师预期的 182 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-06/amazon-results-are-a-sandbag-special-wedbush-s-ives-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 22:49:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Arm 前景令人失望，先锋集团大幅削减费用 | 彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-06/bloomberg-technology-02-06-2025-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Caroline Hyde 和 Jackie Davalos 与首席执行官 Rene Haas 讨论了 Arm 的保守预测。此外，在该公司宣布降低费用之际，与 Vanguard 首席执行官 Salim Ramji 进行了交谈。此外，随着公司用户和参与度下滑，Roblox 股价遭到抛售。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-06/bloomberg-technology-02-06-2025-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 22:43:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊与微软一样表示无法满足人工智能需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/amazon-projects-profit-missing-estimates-on-rising-ai-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司警告投资者，尽管其计划今年投资约 1000 亿美元，但其云计算部门可能面临产能限制，其中大部分资金将用于数据中心、自主研发芯片和其他提供人工智能服务的设备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/amazon-projects-profit-missing-estimates-on-rising-ai-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 21:14:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>假日需求强劲推动预订量增长，Expedia 股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/expedia-posts-strong-holiday-bookings-as-demand-proves-resilient</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Expedia Group Inc. 公布 2024 年最后几个月的总预订量好于预期，反映出冬季假期旅游需求强劲，随后股价在尾盘上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/expedia-posts-strong-holiday-bookings-as-demand-proves-resilient</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 21:05:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对华贸易打压引发航运混乱、价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/how-trump-tariffs-are-affecting-delivery-services-for-shoppers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[物流公司正在努力适应唐纳德·特朗普总统的新规定，这些规定可能会颠覆它们蓬勃发展的从中国卖家向美国买家运送小包裹的业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/how-trump-tariffs-are-affecting-delivery-services-for-shoppers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 10:16:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼暂停特朗普高尔夫球场特区建设</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/indonesia-halts-works-at-special-zone-hosting-trump-golf-course</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于违反环境法规，印尼政府暂停了唐纳德·特朗普品牌豪华高尔夫球场所在的经济特区的建设工程。]]></description>
